      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SANTANOVA (2) won a strong race last start over this course and distance to bring up the hat-trick. The form out of that race has been franked with 2 winners from 4 subsequent starters. This shapes similarly to what she's been winning recently and she can continue her winning ways. CELESTIAL STORM (6) jumped favourite ahead of SANTANOVA last time out and couldn't fend her off, finishing 0.8L behind. She does get a massive weight swing in her favour today however and she'll have the tactical advantage from a good draw. Will be harder to run down this time around. TYCOON HARRY (4) wasn't far behind PINGERS last start and we'll get a good guide on that form earlier in the card. Down in the weights here on the quick turnaround and he can put his best foot forward. CUT THE TALK (1) will find this much easier today and the claim of ZJP comes in handy. Won't be far away. BLACK ORA (3) is better than she showed prior to the break and can return on a positive note.",
